title: Hannah Montana and Miley Cyrus - Best of Both Worlds Concert
description: This is a book of musical scoresOur deluxe songbook matches the soundtrack CD from the wildly popular concert film, presented in Disney Digital 3-D. Features great photos from the movie, and 14 tunes: The Best of Both Worlds * East Northumberland High * G.N.O. (Girl's Night Out) * Good and Broken * I Got Nerve * Just like You * Let's Dance * Life's What You Make It * Nobody's Perfect * Pumpin' Up the Party * Rock Star * See You Again * Start All Over * We Got the Party.
author: Miley Cyrus
